    <body xml:id="Document"><div type="chapter" xml:id="Ch49" n="49"><pb type="VIII_2" n="421"/><head>49.
DE MOTUS LINEA POST CONCURSUM</head>
<head>[Sommer 1673]</head><div type="ueberlieferung"><p><hi rendition="#b #smaller">Überlieferung:</hi>
<list><item><label><hi rendition="#i #smaller">L</hi></label>
<p><hi rendition="#smaller">Aufzeichnung: LH XXXVII 4 Bl. 34. Papierstreifen (23 x 6 cm), unregelmäßig beschnitten. 8 Z. auf Bl. 34 r<hi rendition="#sup">o</hi> und 1 Z. auf Bl. 34 v<hi rendition="#sup">o</hi>. Ein Wasserzeichen.</hi></p><p><hi rendition="#smaller">Cc 2, Nr. 482</hi></p></item></list></p></div><div type="contents">
          <p><hi rendition="#smaller"><hi rendition="#b">Datierungsgründe:</hi> Das Wasserzeichen im Textträger des vorliegenden Stücks ist für den Sommer 1673 nachgewiesen.</hi></p>
        </div><div type="text"><p xml:id="Ch49.p3" rendition="#noindent"><pb type="L"/><fw type="folNum">[34 r<hi rendition="#sup">o</hi>]</fw> Experimentum notabile quo definiri possit, omniane in curvis peragantur per tangentes. Supponamus corpus aliquod linea quadam curva ferri, ut parabolica <hi rendition="#i">ab</hi> aliudque in linea recta ei concurrere, quaeritur post momentum concursus<index indexName="Sachverzeichnis"><term>momentum concursus</term></index>, quaenam futura sit linea motus. Ducatur tangens <hi rendition="#i">bd</hi> crediderit aliquis, cum directio curvae, in puncto <hi rendition="#i">b</hi> sit in tangente <hi rendition="#i">db</hi> aliaque accedat directio in recta <hi rendition="#i">cb</hi> motum esse compositum ex his duabus directionibus. Sed hoc falsum est. Idem enim eveniret, si id verum esset, ac<note type="Afootnote" place="margin" resp="#L"><hi rendition="#i">Links am Rand</hi>: Imo non est absurdum.</note> si corpus <hi rendition="#i">a</hi> in linea recta <app type="Bfootnote"><!--is-correction-app-with-lemma--><lem type="main"><corr resp="#ed">[<hi rendition="#i">db</hi>]</corr></lem><rdg wit="#L"><orig><hi rendition="#i">bc</hi> </orig>  <note type="editorial"><hi rendition="#i">L ändert Hrsg.</hi></note></rdg></app> moveretur, quod est absurdum. Igitur sic potius cogitandum est, motum esse compositum <app type="Bfootnote"><lem type="main">ex</lem><note type="lemma-abbrev">compositum</note><rdg wit="#L" n="1"> in </rdg><rdg wit="#L" n="2"> ex <hi rendition="#i">L</hi></rdg></app> curvilineo illo et rectilineo, <app type="Bfootnote"><lem type="main">aut potius</lem><note type="lemma-abbrev">rectilineo,</note><rdg wit="#L" n="1"> quasi s </rdg><rdg wit="#L" n="2"> aut potius <hi rendition="#i">L</hi></rdg></app> ex tribus illis (pluribusve) directionibus, duabus nimirum (pluribusve) curvam constituentibus <pb type="L"/><fw type="folNum">[34 v<hi rendition="#sup">o</hi>]</fw> et nova rectilinea accedente unde novum curvae genus vel forte prioris curvae nova species.</p><figure rendition="#own-line_centered" xml:id="Ch49.p4">
